;s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Kaitlin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:3:\"uri\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/author/Kaitlin.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"tag:blog.mandrill.com,2016-02-24:/important-changes-to-mandrill.html/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:7:\"summary\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2238:\"<p><strong>Update (3/16/16):</strong> Mandrill is now an add-on for paid monthly MailChimp accounts, and is no longer available as a standalone service. Existing Mandrill users have until April 27, 2016 to merge their Mandrill account with a MailChimp account. See <a href=\"https://mandrill.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/217467117\">this article</a> for additional details, including pricing information and instructions for merging your accounts.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Update (3/4/16):</strong> SparkPost has offered to take on any departing Mandrill users and to <a href=\"https://www.sparkpost.com/pricing\">honor Mandrills pricing</a> for those users.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Update (2/25/16):</strong> Weve published <a href=\"https://mandrill.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/217467117\">an FAQ article</a> in Mandrills Knowledge Base that provides more information about the transition. Well continue updating that article as new questions arise.</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<p>Today, were emailing our customers to announce some significant changes to Mandrill. </p>\n\n<p><strong>Going forward, all Mandrill users will be required to have a paid monthly MailChimp account and verify ownership of all sending domains.</strong> Heres the timeline: Starting 3/16, all new Mandrill users will create accounts through MailChimp, and current Mandrill users can merge their existing Mandrill account with a monthly MailChimp account. Current users will have until 4/27 to merge their accounts.</p>\n\n<h2>Why were making this change</h2>\n\n<p>The MailChimp team built Mandrill in 2012 as a transactional email tool. It was a startup within MailChimp that functioned as a completely separate product. Mandrill is now becoming an optional add-on to paid MailChimp accounts. This is a strategic change were making to close the gap between the two products. MailChimp is designed for marketing, and Mandrill is designed for transactional messages. Each is powerful on its own, and offering Mandrill as an add-on makes MailChimp even more powerful for our small business and e-commerce customers. Our CEO and cofounder Ben Chestnut wrote more about the changes on the <a href=\"http://blog.mailchimp.com/important-changes-to-mandrill\">MailChimp blog</a>.</p>\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"term\";s:13:\"announcements\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"We\'re Making Domain Verification Mandatory\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:4:\"href\";s:73:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/we-are-making-domain-verification-mandatory.html\";s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"2015-08-04T00:00:00Z\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Amanda\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:3:\"uri\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/author/Amanda.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"tag:blog.mandrill.com,2015-08-04:/we-are-making-domain-verification-mandatory.html/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:7:\"summary\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:732:\"<p>We\'re pushing a change today, <strong>August 4, 2015 at 12:00pm UTC</strong> (<a href=\"http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=Domain+Verification+Changes&amp;iso=20150804T12&amp;p1=1440\">see this in your time zone</a>), that makes <a href=\"https://mandrill.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/205582247\">domain verification</a> mandatory when you add a new sending domain and <a href=\"https://mandrill.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/205582267\">set up SPF and DKIM</a>. This change won\'t be applied retroactively, so if you added a domain to your Mandrill account before today and set up SPF and DKIM, we\'ll still sign your mail as usual. However, we still urge you to verify any sending domains for your account.</p>\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"term\";s:13:\"announcements\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"Announcing the Mixpanel Mandrill Connector by Finc3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:4:\"href\";s:72:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/announcing-the-mixpanel-mandrill-connector.html\";s:3:\"rel\";s:9:\"alternate\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:7:\"updated\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"2015-08-03T00:00:00Z\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:6:\"author\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Nathan\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:3:\"uri\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/author/Nathan.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}}s:2:\"id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"tag:blog.mandrill.com,2015-08-03:/announcing-the-mixpanel-mandrill-connector.html/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:7:\"summary\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:820:\"<p><a href=\"https://mixpanel.com/\">Mixpanel</a> is an analytics platform that lets you access detailed data from your website or app, focusing on actions your users take, rather than only showing page views. This means you get powerful data you can manipulate and analyze to get a better understanding of how your users interact with your application or website. Then, you can leverage all of that data and set up sophisticated segments to target your users based on their unique behavior.</p>\n\n<p>Now, thanks to the <a href=\"https://connect.mailchimp.com/integrations/mixpanel-mandrill-connector\">Finc3 Mixpanel Mandrill Connector</a>, you can easily connect Mixpanel and Mandrill to take advantage of Mandrill\'s trusted delivery infrastructure and send trackable, templated emails based on relevant user actions.</p>\n\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"term\";s:12:\"integrations\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"Template Thumbnails and Mobile Preview Improvements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:2:\"en\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:4:\"href\";s:81:\"http://blog.mandrill.com/template-thumbnails-and-mobile-previe