INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (98,1,'2015-05-03 23:20:55','2015-05-03 23:20:55','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">This calculator is intended as a general guide only. The calculations are based on the accuracy of the information provided by you, and are based on various assumptions, including the following: </span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The number of points earned by spending at Fly&nbsp;Buys partners that makes up part of the ‘You Could Be Earning’ result is based on the assumption that you do all of your everyday spending with Fly Buys partners only (for example, all of your grocery shopping is done at New World supermarkets) and is based on current participating companies, qualifying goods and services and points collection rates. Fly Buys and its partners will from time to time determine which goods and services qualify for points collection, any minimum spend and the rate at which points may be collected for purchases of such goods and services. Points calculations are based on the following:</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\">Food and Beverage. $25 = 1 Fly Buys point.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\">Car. Based on an average points collection rate of $21.35 = 1 Fly Buys point calculated by reference to those Fly&nbsp;Buys partners that fall within the category. For Z, a points collection rate of 1 point = $26.78 has been used in the calculation, based on a price of 208.90c per litre for Z Energy 91 petrol, as at <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_1944234953\"><span class=\"aQJ\">31 July</span></span> 2015.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\">Other. Based on average points collection rate of $22 = 1 Fly Buys point calculated by reference to those Fly Buys partners (excluding business partners) that are not included in the food and beverage, car, utilities, pharmacy, home improvements or travel categories.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Power. Based on the average points collection rate of $35 = 1 Fly Buys point. Calculated by reference to those Fly Buys partners that fall within the power category.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Pharmacy. $25 = 1 Fly Buys point.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Home Improvements. Based on an average points collection rate of $28 = 1 Fly Buys point. Calculated by reference to those Fly Buys partners that fall within the home improvement category.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Travel. Based on an average points collection rate of $26 = 1 Fly Buys point calculated by reference to those Fly Buys partners that fall within the travel category.</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\">Insurance. Based on the points collection rate of $20 = 1 Fly Buys point.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The number of points earned on BNZ products that makes up part of the ‘You Could Be Earning’ result is based on the assumption that: </span>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">You have a Fly Buys earning BNZ Classic Visa or MasterCard credit card, and/or a BNZ Fly Buys home loan, and/or BNZ Fly Buys earning insurance; </span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for purchases made with your Fly Buys earning BNZ Classic Visa or MasterCard credit card is 1 Fly Buys point per $40 spent; </span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for your BNZ Fly Buys home loan is 9 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances under $50,000, 34 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances between $50,000 - $149,999 and 84 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances over $150,000; and</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for your Fly Buys earning BNZ Insurance is 1 Fly Buys point for every $20 spent on insurance premium. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Fly Buys collection and redemption rates are subject to change without notice. For further details visit <a href=\"http://www.flybuys.co.nz\">flybuys.co.nz.</a> BNZ (and its related companies) do not guarantee the collection or redemption of Fly Buys points or that Fly Buys points will continue to be offered for products or services provided by them. Credit card and home loan account opening, lending criteria, terms, fees and conditions apply. Insurance terms, conditions, and exclusions apply.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"button-container\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"btn btn-default btn-blue btn-back\" title=\"Back\" href=\"http://flybuyscalculator.beingbui.lt/\">Back</a></p>','Fly Buys Assumptions','','publish','open','open','','fly-buys-assumptions','','','2015-08-24 03:56:36','2015-08-24 03:56:36','',0,'http://bnzcalculator.beingbui.lt/?page_id=98',0,'page','',0);
