ers that fall within the travel category.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The number of points earned on BNZ products that makes up part of the ‘You Could Be Earning’ result is based on the assumption that: </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">You have a BNZ Classic Visa or MasterCard credit card, a BNZ Fly Buys home loan, and BNZ Fly Buys earning insurance; </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for purchases made with your Classic Visa or MasterCard credit card is 1 Fly Buys point per $50 spent; </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for your BNZ Standard/Fly Buys home loan is 9 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances under $50,000, 34 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances between $50,000 - $149,000 and 84 Fly Buys points a month for home loan balances over $150,000; and</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The earn rate for your Fly Buys earning BNZ Insurance is 1 Fly Buys point for every $20 spent on insurance premium. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\"><span class=\"s2\">Fly Buys collection and redemption rates are subject to change without notice. For further details visit flybuys.co.nz. BNZ (and its related companies) do not guarantee the collection or redemption of Fly Buys points or that Fly Buys points will continue to be offered for products or services provided by them. </span><span class=\"s1\">LifeCare (link to:https://www.bnz.co.nz/assets/personal-banking/insurance/pdfs/2015-02-28-lifecare-general-terms.pdf), PremierCare (link to: https://www.bnz.co.nz/assets/about-us/terms-conditions/pdfs/premiercare-insurance-policy-document.pdf) and EasyCover (link to: https://www.bnz.co.nz/assets/about-us/terms-conditions/pdfs/1006-terms-and-conditions-EasyCover-insurance.pdf) insurance terms and conditions apply.) EasyCover Insurance and LifeCare Insurance are underwritten by the insurer, BNZ Life Insurance Limited (“BNZ Life”), and is not an obligation of the 